    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices:
    - Tagline (Beranda): Text display. Goal: Immediate impact. Interaction: Static. Justification: User requirement.
    - About Me (Tentang Saya): Structured text (paragraphs, lists). Goal: In-depth introduction. Interaction: Static. Justification: Standard portfolio section.
    - Skills (Keahlian): Categorized lists, potentially with icons (Unicode/Font Awesome). Goal: Quick assessment of capabilities. Interaction: Static. Justification: Clarity and scannability.
    - Projects (Portofolio): Carousel (HTML/CSS/JS) of project cards (image, title, short desc). Modals (HTML/CSS/JS) for project details (role, challenge/solution, tech, images). Goal: Showcase practical application of skills. Interaction: Carousel navigation, modal open/close. Justification: User requirement for carousel, modals for detailed, focused view without page reload.
    - Articles (Artikel): List of articles (title, summary, link). Goal: Demonstrate research and academic contribution. Interaction: Links to external/downloadable content. Justification: User requirement.
    - Certifications (Sertifikasi): List of certifications. Goal: Validate skills. Interaction: Static. Justification: Standard portfolio section.
    - Contact Form (Kontak): HTML form. Goal: Direct communication channel. Interaction: User input, client-side validation. Justification: User requirement.
    - NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. All visuals are through HTML/CSS structure, Tailwind, Unicode characters, Font Awesome icons, and placeholder images for projects/certificates.
    -->
